
COMMAND:
   portal or portal <living>

ART:
   portal is one if the cleric abilities of a monk to beg
   her/his god to summon a portal to bring her/him and her/his
   friends  to church or another living. This power is only
   available when the monk believes in Illuvatar.
 
COST:
   200 

POWER:
   godgiven 
